data.text:
Death Index

A B C D Mineral County Death Index Last Updated 02/20/2010 03:47:22 PM

Search Suggestions:

1. While in your Internet Browser go to Edit/Find.

Put the surname you are searching for in the window and search that page.

2. Always look for more than one entry in the Index.

3. Look for different spellings of surname.

4. Look to see if the entry may have the surname and given name reversed.

5. When searching for women use married name(s).

6. If all fails email cactusgem.
